title: As the month of the Breast Cancer Awereness is winding down, it doesn't mean we are done and finished...

attachments.displayName:
As the month of the Breast Cancer Awereness is winding down, it doesn't mean we are done and finished. We shall continue with our strong determination towards a happier and joyful living making one small change at a time for the healthier us. We are celebrating this month's Finale on OCTOBER 30, 9pm-10pm, ET, with Prizes and Good company. LIVE!
Join us for Fun, packed with prizes, ONLINE Party. Details here -> http://celebratewomantoday.com/2013/10/25/celebrate-a-cool-cook-in-you-with-brylanehome-online-party/
Thanks +BrylaneHome   and +Celebrate Woman Today
